snippet.title: Welcome to the Abyss - Luna Abyss Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming Soon on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1933000/Luna_Abyss/
Luna Abyss official site: http://www.bonsai-collective.com/luna-abyss
Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/c5839VkW

Luna Abyss is a narrative-driven, first-person action-adventure game. Discover a vast, derelict colony; deep within the belly of an ominous mimic moon. Fight twisted cosmic horrors in intense, fast-paced, bullet-hell combat.
